The paper deals with image tagging, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses user behavior and preferences, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper proposes a new objective function and algorithm for personalized tagging, which could be relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM).
